        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 9‒13. Coillina baka Yin & Peng, 1998 from Chin State, Myanmar (9–10 female, 11–13 male). 9 Epigyne, ventral. 10 Vulva, dorsal. 11–13 Left palp (11 ventral, with arrow indicating thumb-shaped, ventral apophysis; 12 dorsal, with arrow indicating prolateral denticle; 13 retrolateral).Abbreviations: Co—copulatory opening; Cy—cymbium; E—embolus; Eb—embolus base; Fd—fertilization duct; Id—insemination duct; Re—receptacle." ;
